scripts.title: Your Tech-Priest needs help calming her nerves, can you help her?
scripts.synopsis: Your friend from the Adeptus Mechanicus is going to have a big day tomorrow, but asked you to go with her to a bar to calm her nerves, could it be that she wants something more from you?

scripts.title: Evil sorceress gives one of her servants a unforgettable night
scripts.synopsis: The all powerful Sorceress of Ghrond requests that a servant is taken to her chambers, what awaits you there is so much more than you ever expected.
